<p rend="centre"> Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</p>

<p rend="book">Sāsanavaṃsappadīpikā</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Buddhaṃ <pb ed="M" n="0.0001" /> sumālī dvipaduttamo tamo,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Hantvāna bodhesidha paṅkajaṃ kajaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Maggaggaselamhi suñaṭṭhito ṭhito,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">So maṃ ciraṃ pātu sukhaṃ sadā sadā.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Sīhaḷaddīpatoyeva,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Āgatehi disantare;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Bhikkhūhi yācito kassaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Sāsnavaṃsappadīpikaṃ.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Kāmañca porāṇehi yā,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Sāsnavaṃsappadipikā;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Vitthāra vācanāmaggā,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Viracitā vinicchayā.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Sā <pb ed="M" n="0.0002" /> pana mrammasāsāya,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Katattāyeva etesaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Dīpantaranivāsinaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Vahāti suṭṭhunātthaṃ.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Tasmā hi mūlabhāsāya,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Karissāmi ahaṃ have;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Saṃsanditvāna ganthehi,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Taṃ sallakkhentu sādhavoti.</p>

<p rend="subhead">Tatrāyaṃmātikā –</p>

<p rend="indent" n="1"><hi rend="paranum">1</hi>. Navaṭṭhānāgatasāsanavaṃsakathāmaggo,</p>

<p rend="indent" n="2"><hi rend="paranum">2</hi>. Sīhaḷadīpikasāsanavaṃsakathāmaggo,</p>

<p rend="indent" n="3"><hi rend="paranum">3</hi>. Suvaṇṇabhūmisāsanavaṃsakathāmaggo,</p>

<p rend="indent" n="4"><hi rend="paranum">4</hi>. Yonakaraṭṭhasāsanavaṃsakathāmaggo,</p>

<p rend="indent" n="5"><hi rend="paranum">5</hi>. Vanavāsīraṭṭhasāsanavaṃsakathāmaggo,</p>

<p rend="indent" n="6"><hi rend="paranum">6</hi>. Aparantaraṭṭhasāsanavaṃsakathāmaggo,</p>

<p rend="indent" n="7"><hi rend="paranum">7</hi>. Kasmīragandhāraraṭṭhasāsanavaṃsakathāmaggo,</p>

<p rend="indent" n="8"><hi rend="paranum">8</hi>. Mahiṃsakaraṭṭhasāsanavaṃsakathāmaggo,</p>

<p rend="indent" n="9"><hi rend="paranum">9</hi>. Mahāraṭṭhasāsanavaṃsavathāmaggo,</p>

<p rend="indent" n="10"><hi rend="paranum">10</hi>. Cinaraṭṭhasāsanavaṃsakathāmaggocāti.</p>
